LLM Foundations with Python Bounty Showcase

3 steps

These are the top 3 winners of the LLM Foundations with Python Bounty
Join us on Discord

Tutorial Steps

Total steps: 3

  • Step 1: Activity Suggestion Chatbot

    The Activity Suggestion Chatbot was chosen for its innovative approach to enhancing user well-being by combining sentiment analysis, emotion detection, and AI-generated activity suggestions. This personalized experience offers users tailored activities based on their emotional state, providing a unique, mood-responsive interaction.

    Github Repository: https://github.com/gabrielsrs/LLM-foundations-with-python

  • Step 2: Llama-2 Enhanced Chatbot with Sentiment Analysis

    The Llama-2 Enhanced Chatbot with Sentiment Analysis was chosen for its advanced use of the Llama-2 model, which is combined with sentiment analysis and semantic search to provide contextually relevant and emotionally adaptive responses. This integration of various technologies makes the chatbot highly interactive and capable of delivering tailored responses based on the users emotional tone and query context.

    Github Repository: https://github.com/fullendmaestro/Llama-Chatbot

  • Step 3: Customer Support Chatbot

    The Customer Support Chatbot was chosen for its intelligent integration of the Llama-2 model with sentiment and emotion analysis, enabling personalized responses tailored to customer emotions. This approach enhances the chatbots ability to address both emotional and informational needs, making customer interactions more effective and adaptive.

    Colab Notebook: https://colab.research.google.com/drive/1rL1zKoHvS02oafpC6KFxL_kZAeJFY_VU?usp=sharing#scrollTo=c0_5Iz8CPzgP
